        <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-soka-theme-content" class="block block-system block-system-main-block">
  
    
      <div class="ifde-page clearfix">
    

    <div class="ifde-page__inner">

        
        
                <div class="ifde-page__content">
                  <div  class="ifde-page__paragraphs">
        
            <div class="wysiwyg paragraph paragraph--type-wysiwyg paragraph--view-mode-default ds-1col clearfix">

  

  <div class="wysiwyg__content">
          <div  class="wysiwyg__body">
        
            <p><big>Soka University offers students and alumni a campus-wide network of career and professional development opportunities aimed to support the successful transition from college to career and beyond. This hub highlights offices, programs, and resources that develop the <a href="https://www.naceweb.org/career-readiness/competencies/career-readiness-defined/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">core competencies</a> that prepare students for workplace success and lifelong career management. These include Career &amp; Self-Development; Communication; Critical Thinking; Equity &amp; Inclusion; Leadership; Professionalism; Teamwork; and Technology.</big></p>

<p class="text-align-center"><a class="cta--button" href="https://soka.trumba.com/career-readiness-1" rel="noopener" target="_blank">View Upcoming Events</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="cta--button" href="https://rate.soka.edu/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Career Readiness RATE Portal </a></p>

      
  
    </div>


  </div>

</div>


